WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.440 align:middle line:90%


00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:13.870 align:middle line:90%
>> Everybody knows the secret.

00:00:13.870 --> 00:00:22.020 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER] Secret is surrender.

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:26.540 align:middle line:90%


00:00:26.540 --> 00:00:31.470 align:middle line:10%
To really surrender to the
unconditional state of life,

00:00:31.470 --> 00:00:33.650 align:middle line:10%
of creation.

00:00:33.650 --> 00:00:35.560 align:middle line:84%
That is something
to think about.

00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:39.410 align:middle line:90%


00:00:39.410 --> 00:00:43.050 align:middle line:84%
The whole of creation is just
waiting for you to surrender.

00:00:43.050 --> 00:00:46.055 align:middle line:84%
Realize that you're part
of this all that this is.

00:00:46.055 --> 00:00:53.120 align:middle line:90%


00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:54.180 align:middle line:90%
You may leave it.

00:00:54.180 --> 00:00:59.220 align:middle line:10%
You may become estranged from
it and alienated from it.

00:00:59.220 --> 00:01:02.120 align:middle line:10%
But it will always be
there in the present

00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:03.610 align:middle line:10%
until you rediscover it.

00:01:03.610 --> 00:01:24.810 align:middle line:90%


00:01:24.810 --> 00:01:28.583 align:middle line:84%
That's part of the wonderful
mystery of creation.

00:01:28.583 --> 00:01:36.000 align:middle line:90%


00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:39.760 align:middle line:84%
Nothing happens in some past
place or in some future place,

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:42.125 align:middle line:84%
everything happens
exactly in the present.

00:01:42.125 --> 00:01:48.930 align:middle line:90%


00:01:48.930 --> 00:01:57.584 align:middle line:84%
I like my mental body to
just remember to be here now

00:01:57.584 --> 00:02:00.155 align:middle line:90%
that I am here now in this.

00:02:00.155 --> 00:02:07.750 align:middle line:90%


00:02:07.750 --> 00:02:12.290 align:middle line:10%
If your attention is caught
up in the world's doings,

00:02:12.290 --> 00:02:15.700 align:middle line:10%
then it drifts off
the whole time.

00:02:15.700 --> 00:02:21.130 align:middle line:84%
Most of the time we are either
in the past or in the future.

00:02:21.130 --> 00:02:26.920 align:middle line:10%
It's just our mental bodies that
distracts us and alienates us

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:28.710 align:middle line:10%
from being here.

00:02:28.710 --> 00:02:35.018 align:middle line:90%


00:02:35.018 --> 00:02:37.982 align:middle line:90%
[BACKGROUND MUSIC]

00:02:37.982 --> 00:02:54.820 align:middle line:90%


00:02:54.820 --> 00:02:58.000 align:middle line:84%
Well, I think I've experienced
quite a lot of things

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:02.346 align:middle line:90%
that man is prone to experience.

00:03:02.346 --> 00:03:07.330 align:middle line:90%


00:03:07.330 --> 00:03:10.490 align:middle line:84%
Being in public and
feeling the awareness

00:03:10.490 --> 00:03:14.420 align:middle line:84%
of people and their projections,
there was a time in my life

00:03:14.420 --> 00:03:18.655 align:middle line:84%
when these things disturbed me
and really put me off course.

00:03:18.655 --> 00:03:22.580 align:middle line:90%


00:03:22.580 --> 00:03:24.680 align:middle line:84%
The world consists
of the stories

00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:26.720 align:middle line:90%
that people tell each other.

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:30.350 align:middle line:84%
These stories tend
to pin you down,

00:03:30.350 --> 00:03:35.150 align:middle line:84%
and we pin each other down
with our stories as well.

00:03:35.150 --> 00:03:39.296 align:middle line:84%
Our judgments about others and
our judgments about ourselves.

00:03:39.296 --> 00:03:46.880 align:middle line:90%


00:03:46.880 --> 00:03:49.560 align:middle line:90%
And a lot of it is unconscious.

00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:52.220 align:middle line:84%
It's projections
that you receive

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:57.080 align:middle line:84%
from the world around you,
building a reality, which

00:03:57.080 --> 00:03:59.340 align:middle line:90%
is not real at all.

00:03:59.340 --> 00:04:00.505 align:middle line:90%
It's totally invisible.

00:04:00.505 --> 00:04:13.800 align:middle line:90%
[BACKGROUND MUSIC]

00:04:13.800 --> 00:04:18.120 align:middle line:84%
So part of our mental
ability is to go on automatic

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:21.149 align:middle line:84%
and to install stories
inside yourself which

00:04:21.149 --> 00:04:25.460 align:middle line:84%
will keep on reinforcing
certain negative perceptions.

00:04:25.460 --> 00:04:32.100 align:middle line:90%


00:04:32.100 --> 00:04:38.640 align:middle line:84%
You nurture this victimhood
and you nurture this suffering

00:04:38.640 --> 00:04:40.650 align:middle line:84%
as though it belongs to
you, as though you've

00:04:40.650 --> 00:04:42.190 align:middle line:90%
identified with it.

00:04:42.190 --> 00:04:46.800 align:middle line:90%
[BACKGROUND MUSIC]

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:49.170 align:middle line:10%
If you can get out
of that paradigm

00:04:49.170 --> 00:04:52.800 align:middle line:10%
and realize that you must take
responsibility for everything

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:55.980 align:middle line:10%
that happens to you
because it's meant for you.

00:04:55.980 --> 00:04:59.610 align:middle line:84%
Other people can't help you,
you must take responsibility

00:04:59.610 --> 00:05:00.940 align:middle line:90%
for your journey.

00:05:00.940 --> 00:05:08.760 align:middle line:90%
[BACKGROUND MUSIC]

00:05:08.760 --> 00:05:12.330 align:middle line:84%
Where I am and what comes to
me, I must deal with that,

00:05:12.330 --> 00:05:14.190 align:middle line:90%
it's unconditionally.

00:05:14.190 --> 00:05:19.130 align:middle line:84%
I must just deal with
what life is bringing

00:05:19.130 --> 00:05:21.190 align:middle line:90%
to me, putting on my plate.

00:05:21.190 --> 00:05:43.760 align:middle line:90%
[BACKGROUND MUSIC]

00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.703 align:middle line:84%
Everything that life
gives you is a gift.

00:05:46.703 --> 00:05:53.870 align:middle line:90%


00:05:53.870 --> 00:05:56.880 align:middle line:84%
The word love has any
meaning, that's what it means.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:06:00.160 align:middle line:84%
It's an unconditional
surrendering to what is.

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:07.010 align:middle line:90%


00:06:07.010 --> 00:06:10.390 align:middle line:84%
You must unconditionally
accept everyone and everything

00:06:10.390 --> 00:06:11.190 align:middle line:90%
as it is.

00:06:11.190 --> 00:06:16.340 align:middle line:90%


00:06:16.340 --> 00:06:20.400 align:middle line:10%
The moment love is conditioned,
it's no longer love.

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:23.680 align:middle line:84%
There are strings attached,
there are agendas behind it.

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:25.770 align:middle line:84%
So unconditional
love is something

00:06:25.770 --> 00:06:29.526 align:middle line:84%
that really, I think brings
one a bit to a standstill.

00:06:29.526 --> 00:06:36.720 align:middle line:90%


00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:38.490 align:middle line:84%
It means not being
judgmental, it

00:06:38.490 --> 00:06:42.870 align:middle line:84%
means not reacting
immediately to something

00:06:42.870 --> 00:06:47.920 align:middle line:84%
that you find unacceptable or
uncomfortable at that moment,

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.850 align:middle line:90%
but to look again.

00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:56.340 align:middle line:90%


00:06:56.340 --> 00:07:05.615 align:middle line:84%
Love is that intangible
constant of the eternal present.

00:07:05.615 --> 00:07:24.250 align:middle line:90%


00:07:24.250 --> 00:07:28.480 align:middle line:84%
The nation has the
music of Dollar Brand.

