gently they give way
to each other dear

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:51.610 align:middle line:10%
brother I met him of the night
with his arms full of love,

00:07:51.610 --> 00:07:52.410 align:middle line:10%
light.

00:07:52.410 --> 00:07:55.450 align:middle line:90%


00:07:55.450 --> 00:07:58.105 align:middle line:10%
I can't recall the
whole poem just

00:07:58.105 --> 00:08:02.690 align:middle line:10%
that there is this very moment,
but it's really beautiful.

00:08:02.690 --> 00:08:05.460 align:middle line:84%
It's really something
to listen to.

00:08:05.460 --> 00:08:14.320 align:middle line:90%


00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:20.140 align:middle line:84%
I'm grateful to be alive, I
think life is a marvelous gift

00:08:20.140 --> 00:08:23.703 align:middle line:84%
and it's a great paradox
and a great mystery.

00:08:23.703 --> 00:08:27.410 align:middle line:90%


00:08:27.410 --> 00:08:32.633 align:middle line:84%
And yeah, it's just I have
these feelings of gratitude.

